			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>In light of the reactions I've seen to the official Bard Top 10 list that I helped create, I think it's time for us as a community to come together to form a top 10 that comes completely from us.  To this end, I am trying to collect a comprehensive list of all bard issues.  I invite every bard to visit the thread linked below, and post your ideas.
<br />

<br />
I promise to compile a complete list of the bard issues for the next major discussion thread, wherein we can work out which issues are the most critical, and which ones are not important to us as a class.
<br />

<br />
Here is the link:
